**SLIDE 9 — Evaluation Results**

*"I didn't just research this — I ran it. During the evaluation period, Semgrep scanned actual code and automatically blocked pull requests containing critical vulnerabilities before they could reach production. These were not theoretical findings. These were real issues in real code that would have shipped without detection under the current process. Critical findings were caught and stopped at the merge stage — exactly as designed. This is proof of concept. It works."*

